snippet.title: Foobar Zero - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Foobar Zero is an online multiplayer third-person shooter game, with anime-like characters, set in a futuristic world.

Foobar Zero is an indie game developed by a small group in their free time. It is currently under development, and will be free to play when it's released.

For more information visit our website or social media pages.
If you are really interested in the game, you should join our discord server.

Discord: https://discord.gg/kNNYrrpP2Z
Website: https://foobarzero.com/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/foobarzero
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/foobarzero/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/foobarzero
